---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" currentPath="/about">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 pt-20 pb-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Me</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p>
        I'm a tech enthusiast deeply immersed in the AI landscape. My days are spent
        building tools, experimenting with LLMs, and pushing what's possible with
        agent frameworks.
      </p>
      <p>
        From prompt routers to RAG pipelines, I believe the best way to understand AI
        is to build with it. This site is my daily log of that journey.
      </p>
      <h2>What I'm Into</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>LLM tooling and agent frameworks</li>
        <li>Building developer tools for the AI ecosystem</li>
        <li>Exploring model capabilities through practical experiments</li>
        <li>Open source contributions</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
